<p><a name="Open_source_software" id="Open_source_software"></a></p>
<h2><span class="editsection">[<a href="/w/index.php?title=Local_Exchange_Trading_Systems&amp;action=edit&amp;section=19" title="Edit section: Open source software">edit</a>]</span> <span class="mw-headline">Open source software</span></h2>
<p>The following web site software handles offer/want directories transactions and accounting</p>
<ul>
<li><a href="http://project.cyclos.org/site.php" class="external text" title="http://project.cyclos.org/site.php" rel="nofollow">Cyclos</a> Web based complementary currency system build on Java technologies</li>
<li><a href="http://marketplace.matslats.net/" class="external text" title="http://marketplace.matslats.net/" rel="nofollow">Marketplace module for Drupal</a> Social Networking software for community currencies</li>
<li><a href="http://www.fourthcornerexchange.com/" class="external text" title="http://www.fourthcornerexchange.com/" rel="nofollow">Fourth Corner Exchange</a> Trading network and php/mySQL application for LETS</li>
<li><a href="http://www.hughbarnard.org/?q=node/3" class="external text" title="http://www.hughbarnard.org/?q=node/3" rel="nofollow">Cclite</a> Trading system written with Perl/Mysql for LETS, Web and SMS Interface</li>
</ul>


